Congratulations Jamie!
Jamie Sullivan competed in the Special Olympics Virtual State Games for the State of NJ last weekend. She competed in the Track And Field Events for 25m and 50m run. She placed 2nd in the 50m race and She won the 25m race! She is so excited!

Attention UTS Students and Staff:
Would you like to be featured on our school website reciting The Pledge of Allegiance?
If so, please get your parent's permission, video yourself saying the Pledge, and email it to Mrs. Pevorus at rpevorus@uniontwpschool.org. Be sure to include your full name and grade in your email, and if you have an American Flag to feature in your video please display it proudly.
